PrecisEnactment of the INTERNATIONAL TELECOMMUNICATION UNION PRIVILEGES AND IMMUNITIES ORDER - which grants some of the privileges and immunities set out in the Convention on the Privileges and Immunities of the United Nations and in the Vienna Convention on Diplomatic Relations to the Union itself, to its officials and senior officials, to representatives of foreign states and to experts performing missions for the Union.
